{"article_id":"twnhgDQHngFitseb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The White House announced","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"that President Donald Trump will declare a national emergency at the U.S.-Mexico border in an attempt","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to secure his long-desired wall","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"on Thursday .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Congressional aides indicated","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"Trump could seek to divert as much as $ 21 billion from the Pentagon","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"in order to build the wall","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"he has claimed","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Mexico would fund ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"an aggressive move","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"that has already drawn intense criticism from both parties .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Though Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"and Rep. Steve King","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"( R-IA )","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"expressed their support for the plan ,","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"other Republican lawmakers immediately raised concerns about the president ' s latest attempt","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"to save face with his base","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"- questioning both the legality and the precedent","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"it may set for a future Democratic president .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"Sen. Susan Collins","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"( R-ME )","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"told reporters","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that declaring a national emergency","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"to build a border wall","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"would be \" a mistake on the part of the president \" of \" dubious constitutionality . \"","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Sen. Rand Paul","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"( R-KY )","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"voiced similar criticisms ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"noting ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"\" The Constitution ' s pretty clear :","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"spending originates and is directed by Congress ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"so I ' m not really for it . \"","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"In a statement , Sen. Marco Rubio","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"( R-FL )","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" no crisis justifies violating the Constitution \"","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and warned","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that \" a future president may use this exact same tactic","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"to impose the Green New Deal . \"","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Rep. Cathy McMorris-Rodgers","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"( R-WA ) ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"who was the chair of the House Republican Caucus until last month ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"also tweeted a warning about potential implications of Trump ' s precedent .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"seemingly affirmed those concerns ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"as did Sens . Kamala Harris","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and Elizabeth Warren","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"( D-MA ) ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"both 2020 presidential candidates ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"on Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Pelosi , for instance , noted","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"that a Democratic president could use the precedent","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Trump sets","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"with his fabricated emergency","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to declare gun violence a national emergency .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" That ' s a national emergency , \"","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Pelosi told reporters Thursday , the anniversary of the Parkland school shooting .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"\" Why don ' t you declare that emergency , Mr. President ? ... A Democratic president could . \"","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Rep. Jerry Nadler","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"( D-NY ) ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"the chair of the House Judiciary Committee , told the Washington Post","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that Democrats are prepared to take the president to court","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"if he goes through with his plan","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"to circumvent Congress .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"And they ' re not alone -","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"multiple organizations , like Public Citizen and Protect Democracy , said Thursday","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that they are preparing to file lawsuits","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"challenging an emergency declaration .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Trump ' s own Justice Department reportedly told the White House","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"that an emergency declaration for a border wall is \" nearly certain to be blocked by the courts on at least a temporary basis ,","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"preventing immediate implementation of the president ' s plan","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"to pay for the wall . \"","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"since Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"( R-KY )","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"announced the president ' s plan ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"after previously urging him not to take such a step ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"it seems unlikely that Trump will face any real consequences from his party .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Trump accused President Barack Obama of using executive actions","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"to \" subvert the Constitution \" in 2014","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"\" because he is unable to negotiate w/ Congress . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":167,"left":94,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":87,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":0,"right":86,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":86,"left":85,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":85,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purp